$ C:\Program Files\Oracle\VirtualBox\UnattendedTemplates\win_postinstall.cmd

`C:\Program Files\Oracle\VirtualBox\UnattendedTemplates\win_postinstall.cmd` is the *post installation script template for Windows* which runs after the target system has been booted, typically as part of the first login.

